{"title":"利用Zerotier组网实现不同网络环境的主机互通互联","date":"2022-07-29T09:08:52.956Z","slug":"access-intranet-by-zerotier","comments":true,"tags":["CentOS","Zerotier","内网穿透","组网"],"updated":"2023-04-22T13:19:09.643Z","content":"<h4 id=\"0x00：登录-注册\">0x00：登录/注册<a href=\"post/access-intranet-by-zerotier#0x00：登录-注册\"></a></h4><p>打开<a href=\"https://my.zerotier.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">ZeroTier</a>对应操作。</p>\n<h4 id=\"0x01：进入个人中心\">0x01：进入个人中心<a href=\"post/access-intranet-by-zerotier#0x01：进入个人中心\"></a></h4><p>登录即可。</p>\n<h4 id=\"0x02：创建虚拟网络\">0x02：创建虚拟网络<a href=\"post/access-intranet-by-zerotier#0x02：创建虚拟网络\"></a></h4><p><div align=\"left\"><img src=\"/images/20230422/create.png\" alt=\"创建虚拟网络\"></div></p>\n<h4 id=\"0x03：安装客户端\">0x03：安装客户端<a href=\"post/access-intranet-by-zerotier#0x03：安装客户端\"></a></h4><p><div align=\"left\"><img src=\"/images/20230422/install.png\" alt=\"安装客户端\"></div></p>\n<ul>\n<li><p>CentOS</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">curl -s https://install.zerotier.com | sudo bash</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p>Windows<br><code>Windows</code>直接安装<a href=\"https://www.zerotier.com/download/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">下载</a>包。注意：<code>Windows 7</code>和<code>Server 2012</code>安装<a href=\"https://download.zerotier.com/RELEASES/1.6.6/dist/ZeroTier%20One.msi\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">ZeroTier 1.6.6</a></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"0x04：加入虚拟网络\">0x04：加入虚拟网络<a href=\"post/access-intranet-by-zerotier#0x04：加入虚拟网络\"></a></h4><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sudo zerotier-cli join b607网络IDc65d2b09</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><code>Windows</code>直接界面化操作即可。授权通过后<code>ifconfig</code>会绑定上对应的IP地址。</p>\n<p><div align=\"left\"><img src=\"/images/20230422/join.png\" alt=\"加入虚拟网络\"></div></p>\n<h4 id=\"0x05：授权\">0x05：授权<a href=\"post/access-intranet-by-zerotier#0x05：授权\"></a></h4><p>前面复选框选中即可授权通过。</p>\n<p><div align=\"left\"><img src=\"/images/20230422/manage.png\" alt=\"授\"><br>另：还可以建立多个路由，为不同的设备设置固定的内网IP。</div></p>\n<h4 id=\"0x06：测试连通性\">0x06：测试连通性<a href=\"post/access-intranet-by-zerotier#0x06：测试连通性\"></a></h4><p><div align=\"left\"><img src=\"/images/20230422/ping.png\" alt=\"测试连通性\"></div></p>\n","prev":{"title":"基于HLS协议的在线直播流测试地址[1050个](更新时间:2023-04-23)","slug":"hls-test-url"},"next":{"title":"CentOS上通过fdisk分区并挂载硬盘","slug":"mount-disk-on-centos-by-fdisk"},"link":"https://www.alipay.one/post/access-intranet-by-zerotier/"}